('3ab40f91-1e5b-4496-98eb-9d4f5c5661f0', 'the-overheard-opinion-social-soc-socialcasc-13', 'social', 'The overheard opinion (social)', 'You catch a friend describing you to someone else in a way that stings, not maliciously, just honestly. You were not supposed to hear it. There is no clean option.'),
('d281b492-4ed4-4adc-9b1b-3ad05ea19a7b', 'credit-theft-social-soc-socialcasc-14', 'social', 'Credit theft (social)', 'A colleague presents your idea as their own in a room that matters. Correcting it risks looking petty; staying silent cedes the win. The clock is running.'),
