('609819e4-24d7-4efc-a527-654e41794f9a', 'viral-misread-social-soc-socialcasc-22', 'social', 'Viral misread (social)', 'A throwaway message of yours is being screenshotted and reframed out of context. Explaining fuels it; ignoring lets it harden into fact. The clock is running.'),
